---
layout: layouts/page.njk
title: "Infrastructure & uptime"
description: "VoiceTel network infrastructure: colocation facilities, cloud regions, carrier handoffs, redundancy, status visibility, and the voice availability target."
---

<p class="eyebrow">Infrastructure</p>
<h1>Network facts without inflated claims.</h1>
<p class="lede">Six colocation POPs across North America and Europe, plus three cloud regions. Anycast and Geocast routing options. STIR/SHAKEN signing at the edge. 99.99% availability target measured monthly, with the SLA written in plain English.</p>
<p class="hero-actions">
	<a class="btn btn-primary" href="/status/">View status</a>
	<a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/signup/">Free trial</a>
</p>

<section class="section-block">
	<h2>Colocation facilities</h2>
	<div class="oss-cards">
		{%- for c in colocations %}
		<article class="oss-card oss-card--colo">
			<header class="oss-card__header">
				<span class="oss-card__icon">{% icon "buildings" %}</span>
				<h3 class="oss-card__title">{{ c.code }} &mdash; {{ c.city }}{% if c.region %}, {{ c.region }}{% endif %}</h3>
			</header>
			<p class="oss-card__description">
				{%- if c.street %}{{ c.street }} &middot; {% endif -%}
				{{ c.city }}{% if c.region %}, {{ c.region }}{% endif %}{% if c.country %}, {{ c.country }}{% endif %}
			</p>
			{%- if c.compliance and c.compliance.length %}
			<p class="oss-card__meta"><strong>Compliance:</strong> {{ c.compliance | join(", ") }}</p>
			{%- endif %}
			{%- if c.statuscakeTrack %}
			<p class="oss-card__uptime"><img src="https://app.statuscake.com/button/index.php?Track={{ c.statuscakeTrack }}&amp;Days=1000&amp;Design=1" width="200" height="40" alt="{{ c.code }} 1000-day uptime"></p>
			{%- endif %}
		</article>
		{%- endfor %}
	</div>
</section>

<section class="section-block">
	<h2>Cloud regions</h2>
	<div class="oss-cards">
		{%- for r in cloudRegions %}
		<article class="oss-card oss-card--cloud">
			<header class="oss-card__header">
				<span class="oss-card__icon">{% icon "cloud-fill" %}</span>
				<div class="oss-card__heading">
					<h3 class="oss-card__title">{{ r.label }}</h3>
					<p class="oss-card__subtitle"><code>{{ r.awsCode }}</code> &middot; {{ r.geo }}</p>
				</div>
			</header>
			<p class="oss-card__description">{{ r.description }}</p>
			{%- if r.statuscakeTrack %}
			<p class="oss-card__uptime"><img src="https://app.statuscake.com/button/index.php?Track={{ r.statuscakeTrack }}&amp;Days=1000&amp;Design=1" width="200" height="40" alt="{{ r.code }} 1000-day uptime"></p>
			{%- endif %}
		</article>
		{%- endfor %}
	</div>
</section>

<aside class="cta-block">
	<h2>Need procurement-ready details?</h2>
	<p>Route security, redundancy, SLA, and network-design questions through the contact path so support can provide account-appropriate documentation.</p>
	<p class="hero-actions">
		<a class="btn btn-primary" href="/signup/">Try for free</a>
	</p>
</aside>

<p class="uptime-source">Uptime percentages are calculated and displayed by <a href="https://www.statuscake.com/" rel="external">StatusCake</a>.</p>
